@startuml
!define RECTANGLE rectangle

RECTANGLE FastAPI {
    class API {
        - /disk-usage
        - /memory-usage
        - /disk-usage/history
        - /memory-usage/history
    }
    class Database {
        - SQLAlchemy models
        - Database connection
    }
    class Tasks {
        - Periodically fetches disk and memory usage
    }
    class CRUD {
        - Create
        - Read
        - Update
        - Delete operations
    }
    class Schemas {
        - Pydantic models
    }
}

API --> CRUD : Uses
Tasks --> CRUD : Invokes
CRUD --> Database : Uses
@enduml
